---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import InfoBox from '../components/InfoBox.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Vaccinations | Montessa Kennel"
  description="Learn about our vaccination schedule and protocols for our puppies."
  keywords="puppy vaccinations, puppy shots, puppy immunization"
>
  <PageHeader
    title="Vaccinations"
    subtitle="Keeping your puppy healthy and protected"
  />

  <section class="info-content">
    <div class="content-container">
      <h2>Puppy Vaccination Schedule</h2>
      <p>Proper vaccination is essential for your puppy's health. We ensure all our puppies receive age-appropriate vaccinations before going to their new homes.</p>

      <InfoBox type="success" title="Vaccinations Completed Before Adoption">
        <p>Each puppy receives their first round of core vaccinations, typically administered at 6-8 weeks of age. This includes the DHPP vaccine which protects against:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Distemper</li>
          <li>Hepatitis (Adenovirus)</li>
          <li>Parvovirus</li>
          <li>Parainfluenza</li>
        </ul>
      </InfoBox>

      <h3>Recommended Vaccination Schedule</h3>
      <p>Your veterinarian will continue the vaccination schedule after you bring your puppy home:</p>

      <table class="vaccine-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Age</th>
            <th>Vaccines</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>6-8 weeks</td>
            <td>DHPP (1st dose) - Administered by us</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>10-12 weeks</td>
            <td>DHPP (2nd dose)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>14-16 weeks</td>
            <td>DHPP (3rd dose), Rabies</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>12-16 weeks</td>
            <td>Bordetella (if needed)</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <InfoBox type="warning" title="Important">
        <p>Until your puppy completes their full vaccination series, avoid areas where unvaccinated dogs may have been. This includes dog parks, pet stores, and sidewalks in high-traffic areas.</p>
      </InfoBox>

      <h3>Deworming Schedule</h3>
      <p>All puppies are dewormed regularly starting at 2 weeks of age. This protects against common intestinal parasites and ensures your puppy arrives healthy.</p>

      <h3>Records Provided</h3>
      <p>When you receive your puppy, you'll get complete vaccination and deworming records including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Dates of all vaccinations administered</li>
        <li>Vaccine brand and lot numbers</li>
        <li>Deworming medication and dates</li>
        <li>Recommendations for future vaccinations</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="cta-box">
        <h3>Questions About Vaccinations?</h3>
        <p>We're happy to discuss our vaccination protocols with you.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .info-content {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .content-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2a2a2a;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f19645;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #5a5a5a;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    color: #5a5a5a;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .vaccine-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    background: #faf5eb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .vaccine-table th,
  .vaccine-table td {
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e0d5;
  }

  .vaccine-table th {
    background: #f19645;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .vaccine-table tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .cta-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f19645, #e08839);
    color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .cta-box h3 {
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-box p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #e08839;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    background: #d63c3c;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .info-content {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .vaccine-table th,
    .vaccine-table td {
      padding: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }
</style>
